Are certain demographics taking larger or more frequent loans?
Do repeat borrowers behave differently than one-time borrowers?

💰 Loan Performance & Behavior
What is the average loan amount and interest rate?
Are higher loan amounts associated with higher interest rates?
What loan purposes drive the largest loan volumes?

🌍 Regional Analysis
Which regions/states have the highest loan volume?
Are certain regions associated with higher loan sizes or interest rates?
Where are potential growth markets?

⏳ Time Trends
How has loan volume changed year over year?
Are there growth or decline periods?
Any signs of seasonality or spikes?

🧩 Standout Questions 
What combination of customer + region + purpose drives the highest value?
